# Title: Application Termination Attempt via Wmic.EXE
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2023-09-11
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects an attempt to terminate a process via "wmic" with the "call terminate" flag. Adversaries may
# use wmic to terminate security products or other applications on the compromised host. This event is
# triggered on on attempt and process creation can be either successful or unsuccessful.
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.t1047
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_wmic_terminate_application.yml

CommandLine="*call*" CommandLine="*terminate*" Image="*\\WMIC.exe" OR OriginalFileName="wmic.exe"